sets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T22:44:02.000Z","msg":"係你個校監好，唔係度度d啊頭都會examine件事<br />\n值得恭喜，但係香港真係唔係次次得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T04:48:07.000Z","msg":"係啊<br />\n我聽我啲舊同事講<br />\n其實間間都係咁<br />\n呢行真係好冇保障<br />\n有個單元重要教班仔話我是中國人、五星紅旗在飄揚等等<br />\nDklm<br />\n我頂唔順轉咗行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b87aef0989894a9e902fd63e6cacc711b65b3d80","tid":1811141,"uid":34927,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T04:48:51.000Z","msg":"屌好撚明<br />\n跟著個無料上司 靠自己senior就乜野程序都唔跟 expect個新仔乜柒都識自己攪店<br />\n一開始就已經係自己摸索，完全無交更無教學，日日返工比老細屌d野亂柒咁做。唔識就梗係做撚錯嫁，做錯左又無個上司睇住，做條撚咩。<br />\n依家做左半年，d野開始上手識做，個上司就開始笑笑口對住我氹下我<br />\n食撚屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7131f3bb14aa5bf06a037988a5ffdc7b5b2d582c","tid":1811141,"uid":121580,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bc814e8246c0134d120ebf1eed88f4251b982266","tid":1811141,"uid":17777,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"c1efd764afc9aba23bb151a08ce551ea8c1bb4d7","tid":1811141,"uid":265756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T12:10:01.000Z","msg":"大家share 牙下<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T18:57:55.000Z","msg":"上一份工同你情況好撚相似<br />\n<br />\n直屬上司係on9 真係慘撚到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔撚教又要你識 到錯果時就淨係識屌<br />\n最撚慘係佢本身做野又冇料 如果有料條氣都順啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T04:51:47.000Z","msg":"咩都叫你做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又唔撚講點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n問佢又話出埋你份糧好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做完又屌有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後個次次都HEA做+最後個日先交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n早D做完俾佢特別多奇怪要求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n明明自己阻住哂,開會就話人唔做野<br />\n起初大老細覺得佢好有氣勢,以為佢做到野<br />\n後期都知佢係玩野唔做野,屌柒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df287c092465aacf58fd4fec42ed9e6591a14673","tid":1811141,"uid":49004,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f9de7be2bb01e1fb8700cb630d603b090a369c8f","tid":1811141,"uid":42762,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T17:12:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T04:54:16.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好信啲阿頭懶好人講野<br />\n只係佢地一套處世技巧<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84ec2ffddf769c2892c96c38f849ef84e3040525","tid":1811141,"uid":54126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e51e2691c4bf4f30f350de414687861cb3dd4aa5","tid":1811141,"uid":52670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T13:04:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>比人撚都仲要等一年？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />立即搵工，搵到份新工娜娜聲閃啦</blockquote>你估而家咁易搵工咩<br />\n如果差唔多一年做夠先走啦</blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T06:08:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adcb88f728c647e23ff1fd5b8a283c02a4ad1c94","tid":1811141,"uid":310386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T06:10:37.000Z","msg":"佢做到就唔洗請你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}